Three nice-size bedrooms & huge game area upstairs. Privacy w/corner lot. Enjoy the back yard covered patio. Walking distance to elementary school...NISD school district. Shopping near by but quiet at home. Strategically located to LAFB/Camp Bullis...easy access to major highways to anywhere in SA & SAMMC/RAFB
